                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17920113-1-off1 t17920113-1-cd2"></join> last, and putting him in fear, and feloniously taking from his person, and against his will, one man's hat, value 2 s. 6 d. the goods of the said 
